    "details": {
      "biography": {
        "value": "<p>Rot-touched are humanoids who survived direct Rot exposure — not killed, but twisted beyond recognition into animalistic, hunger-driven undead. Their flesh is partially decomposed, reeking of decay and infection, their bodies bent into unnatural shapes by corruption. They hunt the bloodied and the weak, their Hunger growing sharper when prey falls below half Hit Points. Their Corrupted Claw poisons targets, and their Rot Spray can slow an entire cluster of heroes at range.</p>",
        "public": ""
